title: $895 / 1br - Wyandotte- Spacious 1 Bedroom 1 Bath Unit Available Now!
posting_body: ['Are you looking for a beautiful apartment?', 'Look no further than this', 'updated 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom unit.', 'This unit features a spacious layout with an updated dining area, spacious bedrooms, fresh paint, appliances in the kitchen, and subway tiling.', 'This spacious apartment is located in the beautiful City of Wyandotte, close to the Downtown area.', 'No Pets allowed.', 'Apartment Features:', '-1 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom', '-Modern Kitchen with White Cabinets, Subway Tiling, & Granite Countertops', '- Appliances Include Refrigerator, Dishwasher,& Oven,', '-Hardwood Floors', '-Off-street Parking', 'Available Now!!', '$895 Monthly Rent', '$895 Security Deposit', 'Also enjoy features such as Online rent payment, online maintenance requests, and online applications.', 'Thank you for your interest', 'For more information or to schedule an appointment for a showing please call', 'show contact info', '!']
